    "note": "[provenance:hand-derived §6.2 + AOZORA-ANNOTATION 2026-06-17] Bare range 点/線 markers pair by family (§7.1): 傍点, 二重傍線, and a 左に-prefixed left-side 傍線 each wrap their run. Offsets from the §3 byte model; not read back from a processor. Canonical serialize folds the bare inline range to the forward form `…［＃「…」に〈kind〉／の左に〈kind〉］` (ADR 0003); a 点/線 family mismatch or non-text content stays a container."
  },
